br.com.site.survey

Class ImageTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.site.survey.ImageTool

  • public abstract class ImageTool
extends java.lang.Object
    This class can be used to convert images. Note that all the methods of this class are declared as static. Supports the following image operations
    • Convert between Image and BufferedImage
    • Split images
    • Resize image
    • Create tiled image
    • Create empty transparent image
    • Create a colored image
    • Flip image horizontally
    • Flip image vertically
    • Clone image
    • Rotate image
    Author:
    Sri Harsha Chilakapati
